    <tier id="COLLOQ_ROG-dialog-0042" speaker="ROG-dialog-0042" category="colloq" type="a" display-name="ROG-dialog-0042 [colloq]">
      <event start="T2-457" end="T1">Dober je. </event>
      <event start="T1" end="T4-28">Misl@m, da je to to. </event>
      <event start="T5-717" end="T2">Eee </event>
      <event start="T2" end="T7-173">bok. </event>
      <event start="T8-184" end="T8-976">Kva je zdej? </event>
      <event start="T8-976" end="T9-551">Kaku si? </event>
      <event start="T10-106" end="T11-567">Lej, </event>
      <event start="T11-567" end="T16-565">zd@le dejma k@kšno stvar rečt ta prvo mmm okrog ... </event>
      <event start="T16-565" end="T22-867">Se spomneš, ko smo šli takr@t eee leta sedemindevetdeset, </event>
      <event start="T22-867" end="T4">al je blu sedemindevetdeset </event>
      <event start="T4" end="T25-8">al je blo kej kasnej? </event>
      <event start="T33-291" end="T5">In to je blo, </event>
      <event start="T5" end="T6">če se ne mot@m, </event>
      <event start="T6" end="T7">je blu to za Bežigradom, </event>
      <event start="T7" end="T38-328">je tako? </event>
      <event start="T40-390" end="T9">Ej, </event>
      <event start="T9" end="T10">spomn@m se, </event>
      <event start="T10" end="T44-666">takr@t nas je foter pelu, </event>
      <event start="T44-666" end="T11">men je blo to tku čist abstraktnu. </event>
      <event start="T11" end="T12">Sploh nisem vedu, kam gremo. </event>
      <event start="T12" end="T52-378">Itak v Lublano, kadarkoli smo šli, smo se vedno zgub@l. </event>
      <event start="T52-933" end="T53-25">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T53-25" end="T56-876">Tko da p() po mojem smo šli tist dan itak ene sedem ur prej. </event>
      <event start="T58-46" end="T59-052">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T59-052" end="T59-55">Taku da ... </event>
      <event start="T65-377" end="T66-371">A jih je blo tok? </event>
      <event start="T69-487" end="T22">Pač vem, d smo pol t@m, k smo sedel, smo sedel na tistih tribunah, </event>
      <event start="T22" end="T23">pa se mi je zdelo ogromno, </event>
      <event start="T23" end="T24">ampak zdej če, če gledaš ta stadion eee za Bežigradom, </event>
      <event start="T24" end="T25">sploh ni taku vel@k, </event>
      <event start="T25" end="T26">ne, </event>
      <event start="T26" end="T80-604">v bistvu primerjavi s k@kšnim drugim. </event>
      <event start="T80-604" end="T27">Eee </event>
      <event start="T27" end="T28">ampak tak@t je blu to uno vau, </event>
      <event start="T28" end="T83-017">ne. </event>
      <event start="T83-845" end="T29">In eee ja, </event>
      <event start="T29" end="T30">to je bil, to je bil po mojem je bil to moj p@ru tak večji koncert. </event>
      <event start="T30" end="T31">Lahku, da smo k@kš@nga t() tazga lokal@nga mel še prej, </event>
      <event start="T31" end="T92-073">samu ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T98-975" end="T100-124">Aha. </event>
      <event start="T107-06" end="T107-878">Misl@š? </event>
      <event start="T109-889" end="T38">Ah, kje, </event>
      <event start="T38" end="T110-721">ne spomn@m se. </event>
      <event start="T110-721" end="T111-671">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T111-671" end="T112-246">vem, kje je, </event>
      <event start="T112-246" end="T113-095">sam se ne spomn@m. </event>
      <event start="T126-252" end="T43">Ck a ona je tak@t še ... </event>
      <event start="T43" end="T44">Ja ja, </event>
      <event start="T44" end="T45">vem. </event>
      <event start="T45" end="T129-377">Ona je tak@t dobila karte </event>
      <event start="T129-833" end="T131-003">in eee ... </event>
      <event start="T131-003" end="T134-794">Ja pa midva sma misl@m da r() res glih takr@t to ful poslušala. </event>
      <event start="T134-794" end="T137-548">Taku da je blu, je je je glih je glih prov pršlo. </event>
      <event start="T143-156" end="T54">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T54" end="T145-098">foter ni bil glih za to zvrst. </event>
      <event start="T145-098" end="T55">On je, on bi bolj na k@kšne k@kšne druge koncerte hotu it, </event>
      <event start="T55" end="T510">ampak normalno, </event>
      <event start="T510" end="T56">ni n@s pa mogu same pust@t, </event>
      <event start="T56" end="T151-201">ne. </event>
      <event start="T151-696" end="T57">Eem </event>
      <event start="T57" end="T58">js sem bil takr@t st@r ene, </event>
      <event start="T58" end="T59">kuk, </event>
      <event start="T59" end="T156-333">ene mmm osem let, devet, </event>
      <event start="T156-333" end="T158-691">ti pa dvanajst, trinajst. </event>
      <event start="T162-04" end="T64">Ck ja, taku, </event>
      <event start="T64" end="T65">sta šla, </event>
      <event start="T65" end="T163-308">ja. </event>
      <event start="T163-308" end="T66">No, </event>
      <event start="T66" end="T168-193">ampak p@ru letu, ko smu šli, jjj eee s spomn@m, da mi je, da mi je tko ... </event>
      <event start="T168-193" end="T67">K@ po navad tak mejh@n otrok nt na koncertu, </event>
      <event start="T67" end="T511">dober, </event>
      <event start="T511" end="T68">nisem bil zdej ful mejh@n, </event>
      <event start="T68" end="T172-383">amp@k mi, mi ni n@č dolg trajalo. </event>
      <event start="T172-383" end="T175-944">Je kr lepo minilo. </event>
      <event start="T177-165" end="T178-116">Ni, ni blu unu ... </event>
      <event start="T181-009" end="T181-675">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T185-388" end="T186-628">Kjerga ni blo? </event>
      <event start="T187-529" end="T188-222">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T189-015" end="T74">Viš, </event>
      <event start="T74" end="T190-105">to sem ... </event>
      <event start="T190-105" end="T191-234">Tu je tebe ful motil, </event>
      <event start="T191-234" end="T192-054">a ne da? </event>
      <event start="T197-761" end="T198-256">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T204-617" end="T205-381">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T206-802" end="T207-105">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T209-404" end="T82">Ja sam zakva? </event>
      <event start="T82" end="T210-93">Pa zakva pa ni pršu? </event>
      <event start="T221-106" end="T514">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T514" end="T221-770">blu je, </event>
      <event start="T221-770" end="T223-771">takr@t je že blu proti konc tist() tistga prv@ga, prve runde. </event>
      <event start="T223-771" end="T227-843">Sicer so pol še, še neki so pol delal kasnej. </event>
      <event start="T227-843" end="T88">Eee </event>
      <event start="T88" end="T89">js se tega sicer ne spomn@m, da ga ni blu, </event>
      <event start="T89" end="T232-333">tku da mene tu očitno že ni motilu. </event>
      <event start="T232-333" end="T232-973">Vem pa, da itak jih je eee so mel tut neke dodatne glasbenike na odri, </event>
      <event start="T232-973" end="T91">ne, </event>
      <event start="T91" end="T90">tku da ni jih blo samo osem, </event>
      <event start="T90" end="T237-803">ne. </event>
      <event start="T245-886" end="T246-464">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T248-997" end="T250-245">Ja ja ja ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T255-218" end="T256-332">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T256-332" end="T100">In kaj to, to se ti je, to se ti je zdelo ful bedno, </event>
      <event start="T100" end="T259-359">ne? </event>
      <event start="T263-445" end="T102">Ja itak, </event>
      <event start="T102" end="T103">midva nisma druzga ... </event>
      <event start="T103" end="T268-06">Js sem si zarad njega ddd dolge lase puščol takr@t. </event>
      <event start="T269-161" end="T269-937">Jo. </event>
      <event start="T270-672" end="T105">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T105" end="T271-623">to so bli, </event>
      <event start="T271-623" end="T272-057">tu so bli ... </event>
      <event start="T272-495" end="T273-636">cajti, ja. </event>
      <event start="T279-785" end="T280-457">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T280-457" end="T283-808">K se spomniš tistga postra, k so bli na neki plaži </event>
      <event start="T283-808" end="T288-101">po pa j() so mel vse neke rdeče noge, k so po kamnih hodil, [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T288-101" end="T289-698">po je blu pa to na sliki? [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T289-908" end="T292-027">Veš, k@k z z nekim morjem pa neki tazga, </event>
      <event start="T292-027" end="T293-839">v kopalkah so bli. </event>
      <event start="T294-664" end="T298-112">Ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T298-112" end="T109">možno, ja, </event>
      <event start="T109" end="T299-4">da t@m, kt so, so istočasno j() mel eee fotošuting. </event>
      <event start="T307-199" end="T308-34">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T517" end="T309-668">Mhm. </event>
