      <event start="T1311-055" end="T1315-201">In smo pol to majčkeno iz eee iz() [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T1319-587" end="T1319-944">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1333-961" end="T1334-609">Ta mala sploh še jih nikoli ni, nikoli zares poslušala </event>
      <event start="T1334-609" end="T1338-378">in se je kar odločila, da jih ne mara. </event>
      <event start="T1338-378" end="T543">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T543" end="T459">to, to ne sme se tako. </event>
      <event start="T459" end="T1340-855">To ne smeš otroke tako vzgajati, </event>
      <event start="T1340-855" end="T460">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T460" end="T1342-559">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1343-487" end="T1343-842">Je() ()beštrga, </event>
      <event start="T1343-842" end="T1344-98">to ni dobro, </event>
      <event start="T1344-98" end="T1345-799">glej. </event>
      <event start="T1345-799" end="T461">To se mora otrok sam odločiti. </event>
      <event start="T461" end="T462">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T462" end="T463">glej, </event>
      <event start="T463" end="T464">to je, to je prekrasno, če lahko otrok sam reče: </event>
      <event start="T464" end="T1351-128">"Daj mi en komad," </event>
      <event start="T1351-128" end="T1352-396">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T1352-396" end="T466">"tako bolj žestoki," </event>
      <event start="T466" end="T467">ne. </event>
      <event start="T467" end="T468">Jaz bom, jaz tudi svoji ta mali rečem: </event>
      <event start="T468" end="T469">"Glej, </event>
      <event start="T469" end="T470">če ti kaj paše, </event>
      <event start="T470" end="T471">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T471" end="T472">samo povej, </event>
      <event start="T472" end="T473">glej, </event>
      <event start="T473" end="T474">bomo vse zrihtali," </event>
      <event start="T474" end="T1359-027">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1359-027" end="T475">Zadnje cajte najbolj ima rada muzikal od Lion Kinga, </event>
      <event start="T475" end="T1362-238">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1364-380" end="T1365-926">Veš, kako so pele v avtu. </event>
      <event start="T1365-926" end="T1367-228">Aaj. </event>
      <event start="T1367-228" end="T478">Jah, </event>
      <event start="T478" end="T1368-966">pele so skup. </event>
      <event start="T1368-966" end="T1370-508">Circle of Life pa tako. </event>
      <event start="T1370-508" end="T1371-201">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1378-017" end="T484">To ga pa ni, </event>
      <event start="T484" end="T1380-809">ne. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T1385-718" end="T1387-247">Po mojem je, je to, </event>
      <event start="T1387-247" end="T1388-551">bom rekel ... </event>
      <event start="T1392-259" end="T1392-772">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1394-576" end="T488">Pa ja, </event>
      <event start="T488" end="T1399-787">saj je še bil kak koncert oziroma lokal(), lokalni so sigurno še bili, </event>
      <event start="T1399-787" end="T1401-362">ne eee .... </event>
      <event start="T1401-362" end="T1404-096">Ampak eee ja. </event>
      <event start="T1404-096" end="T1407-654">Hala Tivoli Seal dva osem. </event>
      <event start="T1409-004" end="T490">Tako, </event>
      <event start="T490" end="T491">no, </event>
      <event start="T491" end="T492">tudi plac sam za koncerte bolj tako, </event>
      <event start="T492" end="T493">no, </event>
      <event start="T493" end="T1412-952">ampak, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1413-963" end="T494">Smo šli. </event>
      <event start="T494" end="T1416-38">Pa jaz sem bil na Juliu Iglesiasu. </event>
      <event start="T1417-842" end="T1420-697">On je imel tudi eee r() delaye na, na, na ... </event>
      <event start="T1421-07" end="T496">Uuu, </event>
      <event start="T496" end="T1422-835">je rekel, </event>
      <event start="T1422-835" end="T497">je rekel: </event>
      <event start="T497" end="T498">"Crazy," </event>
      <event start="T498" end="T1427-086">pa je še dve minuti [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T1427-086" end="T1428-453">Je tako. </event>
      <event start="T1429-622" end="T500">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T500" end="T501">pol četrtega, Kovak, greva pa na Mi2, k imajo tridesetletnico, </event>
      <event start="T501" end="T1433-387">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1433-387" end="T1435-281">Tako da bo kar, </event>
      <event start="T1435-281" end="T502">bo kar zanimivo, </event>
      <event start="T502" end="T1436-509">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1437-361" end="T503">Tako da nič, </event>
      <event start="T503" end="T504">glej, </event>
      <event start="T504" end="T505">se slišimo, </event>
      <event start="T505" end="T506">ne, </event>
      <event start="T506" end="T507">spet ob priliki, </event>
      <event start="T507" end="T1440-552">no, </event>
      <event start="T1440-552" end="T1441-067">pa drži se, </event>
      <event start="T1441-067" end="T1441-919">no. </event>
      <event start="T1442-969" end="T508">Dobro, </event>
      <event start="T508" end="T1444-217">ajde, živjo. </event>
      <event start="T1444-217" end="T1445-010">Bok. </event>
    </tier>
